S.FORM: saysanian 賽山藍 u siwkay nu nipaluma kagak kakuniza(Hulam: ke xue fen lei) salaedan(cei): Plantae panan : Magnoliophyta upiz : Magnoliopsida mata : Lamiales sapamat(ke): Acanthaceae mikitinay(su): Blechum hicahicaay(cong): B. pyramidatum u sanek nu nipaluma malaheci tu imelang pasubana i cacudadan a lacul u zuma a cidekay a kamu, saungay misapayu' a cidekay u sulit nu zuma a kamu-Hulam atu Amilika

saysanian 賽山藍 o siwkay no nipaloma kagak kakoniza(Holam: ke xoe fen lei) salaedan(cei): Plantae panan : Magnoliophyta opiz : Magnoliopsida mata : Lamiales sapamat(ke): Acanthaceae mikitinay(so): Blechom hicahicaay(cong): B. pyramidatom o sanek no nipaloma malaheci to imelang pasobana i cacodadan a lacol o zoma a cidekay a kamo, saongay misapayo' a cidekay o solit no zoma a kamo-Holam ato Amilika
